block content
	div(id='topbar', class='navbar navbar-default')
		p
			a(href='/', id='title') [ API Project ]
			span(id='author') By Agust√≠n Balmer
	div(id='main-full')
		p API: File Metadata Microservice

		p User stories:
			ul
				li I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.
				li When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response.

		p Example output:
			br
			| {"size":770}

		p Usage:
		form(action="/upload", method="post", enctype="multipart/form-data")
			input(class='btn btn-default', type="file", name="file")
			br
			input(class='btn btn-default', type="submit")